word_mean_info__list.difference: 指将人或物朝出力者的方向拖，不涉及力的大小，含平稳意味，常作借喻用。
特指用绳子或链条等拖或拉本身无动力或无法使用自身动力的东西。
最普通用词，包含本组其它各词的一些意思，可指朝各个方向拉，侧重一时或突然拉动的动作。
指沿斜坡而上或水平方向缓慢地拖或拉十分沉重的人或物。作借喻时可指把人硬拉扯过来。
指用力拖或拉，不涉及方向，多作航海用词。
多指一阵阵地用力拖或拉，但不一定使被拉的人或物移动。

bilingual.source: She watched him drag the chair across the room.
bilingual.target: 她看着他把椅子拖过房间。

bilingual.source: Drag the icon to the trash to delete the file.
bilingual.target: 将图标拖到垃圾桶以删除文件。

bilingual.source: They had to drag the fallen tree off the road.
bilingual.target: 他们不得不把倒下的树拖离道路。
他们一起拖拽那条大网。

bilingual.source: The puppy likes to drag its toy.
bilingual.target: 小狗喜欢拖拽它的玩具。

bilingual.source: He tried to drag the heavy table.
bilingual.target: 他用力拖拽那张沉重的桌子。

bilingual.source: Don't drag your feet when you walk.
He reluctantly drag his feet towards school.
bilingual.target: 他不情愿地拖拽着脚步走向学校。

bilingual.source: She had to drag her luggage through the airport.
bilingual.target: 她不得不拖拽行李穿过机场。

list.abstract: 《DRAG》是由Orontes Games制作发行的一款赛车竞速类游戏。

yingyinNormal.en: Wait. No, no. Drag me down. Drag me down.
You'll have to drag me out of here because I'm not giving that statement.
yingyinNormal.zh: 恐怕你得把我拖出去了，因为我不会做那个声明。

yingyinNormal.en: I got a boutonniere. If you're getting cold feet, I will drag you up there myself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我连胸花都买了。如果你敢临阵脱逃，我绝对会亲自拖你上去。

yingyinNormal.en: It's time everyone knew. Drag me back. Go ahead. Here we go. Why would you do that?
yingyinNormal.zh: 是该向大家承认的时候了，把我拖回去吧，咱们走吧，你干嘛这样?

yingyinNormal.en: No, no. You are doing great. Don't you give up. That's why we didn't tell you, and we won't drag you down with us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不行，你戒烟很成功，不许放弃，所以我们才没跟你说，我们不想拖你下水。

yingyinNormal.en: What you do is you just drag your nets along the bottom. On a good day, you can catch over a hundred pounds of shrimp.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你只需要沿着海底拖你的网，在一个好天气，你一次就能捕到上百磅的虾。

yingyinNormal.en: My brain may be evolved, but my tongue still wants to pick up a club and drag that truck back to my cave.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的大脑已经进化完毕，但我的舌头还是想捡起一根木棒把那小摊敲晕再拖回我的山洞。

yingyinNormal.en: I mean it was so cute, it would sit in my lap and just purr all day long, and I would drag a shoestring on the ground and he would chase it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 超可爱的，躺在我的膝盖上，整天满足地喵喵叫，我还会拿鞋带在地上拖，让它追着跑。

yingyinNormal.en: A sea anchor is used as a drag to keep the boats head to the wind.
yingyinNormal.zh: 海锚能起到拖拽的作用，让船能迎风行驶。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, who should I blame? The nice bell man who had to drag out luggage to 10 different rooms?
yingyinNormal.zh: 否则该怪谁？那个拖着行李跑了10间房的倒霉服务生？

yingyinNormal.en: Two minutes. And then I'll come out and drag you in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 2分钟，然后我会出来拉你进去。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you, even if I did have to drag it out of you myself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢，虽然这是我逼你说出来的。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm surprised he hasn't tried to drag you in. My God, he has.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他竟然没想拉你下水吗？天哪，他还真这么干了。

yingyinNormal.en: Patrick says they make me look like a leprechaun drag queen. He was being nice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 帕特里克说我看起来像个又矮又老的变装皇后。他很委婉。

yingyinNormal.en: But, you know, every time someone rises up in this world, there's always gonna be some asshole trying to drag him down.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过 每次有人发达了，势必会有混蛋会想方设法把他拉下去。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, he doesn't have to know. It's not like we run in the same circles. I hang out with you guys, and he stars in a drag show in Vegas.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他不需要知道，我们的生活圈不一样，我跟你们来往，而他，他在拉斯维加斯表演变装秀。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you gonna dress in drag in front of your fiancee? Yeah. We have no secrets from each other. Well, except for the fact that I crocheted this myself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你要在你未婚妻面前男扮女装吗？是啊。我们之间没有任何秘密。除了这是我自己手工编织出来的。
